title: Alien Outpost. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: January 30th, 2015

Description:

Two documentary cameramen are embedded in an army unit in the most hostile place on earth, an outpost surrounded by the last remaining alien fighters (Heavies) of an invading attack force. The world may have forgotten about the Outposts, but the Heavies are planning the second invasion of Earth, and the soldiers are the only ones who can stop it. This brilliant sci-fi action thriller is the directorial debut of Jabbar Raisani, an award-winning F/X artist for 'Game of Thrones.'

Director: Jabbar Raisani

Writers: Jabbar Raisani, Blake Clifton

Actors: Adrian Paul, Joe Reegan, Reiley McClendon, Rick Ravanello

Genre: Thriller, Science Fiction

Run Time: 1 hour 35 minutes
